      <title>泛大西洋资本集团领投 Startup Insider 5 亿美元融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/general-atlantic-leads-500-million-funding-for-startup-insider</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Insider 是一家利用人工智能的全球营销技术平台，在由泛大西洋资本集团领投的一轮融资中筹得 5 亿美元，这笔现金流入将支持其在美国扩展业务的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/general-atlantic-leads-500-million-funding-for-startup-insider</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
